commit.message:
Exclude "tests" directory from composer classmap

The test is not needed in the classmap, and it raised a warning
with composer v1.10 when autoloader optimization is enabled.

Resolves: https://github.com/pear/Console_CommandLine/pull/10

Fix #21063: Support more xmlschema.rng locations (for composer installations)

http://pear.php.net/bugs/bug.php?id=21063
fix test suite, object numbers may differ

Fix comparison on PHP 7.

In PHP7 an empty string is not identical (===) to false, so the
comparison should be with == instead of ===
Fix bug #19921: package dependencies don't include dom
